{
  "stem": "7546.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although, in our part of Poland, September is not so hot anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were going down south, towards Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Auschwitz is west of Krakow-- west or south-- southwest of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We arrived early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't light yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The train stopped, and the getting off the train [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] was hell on Earth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "First of all, you had prisoners that were there before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were wearing striped uniforms with striped hats.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they tell us, out!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you don't go out faster, you'll get hit, you'll get killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everybody out, everybody out!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we walked out of the train-- it was a cattle train, of course, it wasn't a passenger train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a cattle train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were packed like cattle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got off the train amid shots-- there was shooting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dogs were jumping and barking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The German was screaming with the most profane language imaginable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they held in their hand those leather straps that you use when you ride a horse, hitting and beating without any pity.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they'd tell-- men separate, women separate, men separate, women separate, men separate, women separate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we listened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The men go separately, the women go separately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we formed a line, walking towards the end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the women were also walking towards the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a German officer, whether it was Mengele or not, I don't know-- we were walking towards him, and he held that leather strap in his hand, and it was folded in half.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Right, left, right, left, left, right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now it was quite obvious at that time that the people that were going right were people like me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They still looked like a human being.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
